Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.projectmanagement.properties

Class TemplateProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.projectmanagement.properties.TemplateProperties
Direct Known Subclasses:
TemplateRequestBody
public class TemplateProperties extends Object
TemplateProperties defined the properties that can be overridden from the template object when creating an object from a template.
